,Arial" SIZE=1>21</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>2/2/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>3:05:49 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Ogre stun protection</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">How much does this improve ogre warrior over other warriors?<br>
</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/udinadian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>dinadian</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>knows that Warriors are Superior</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>10</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>2/3/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>1:24:05 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Ogre stun protection</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Well,  they can't be stunned by any melee attack from the front.  Even at low levels when tanking against skels or madmen you can get stunned resulting in a potential loss of an attack for you.  I suppose that this would be most useful against warrior type MOBs or dueling someone that can bash, slam or stunkick.  The funny thing is that a lot of ogres don't even realize the have this capacity which indicates that some chnge in tactics are indicated in order to make the best use of it.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2F2F4F><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/utugorisfat.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tugor is fat</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>knows that Warriors are Superior</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>43</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>2/4/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>9:57:27 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://facelink.com/K95152?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Ogre stun protection</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">It's pretty good for dueling.  I was dueling (stood in front of each other and traded hits) a level 60 Troll Warrior with almost full beserkers, CoCW, and some exquisite velium weapons vs my 1044 self buffed AC and Lam+Club of the Ice Ocean combo... got him down to half a bub when he finally killed me because I stunned him so much while he couldn't stun me =P  Other than that, it just lets you do more damage because you aren't getting stunned fighting a mob.<br>
<br>
-Tugor</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=nubb>Nubb</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>knows that Warriors are Superior</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>2</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>2/10/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>8:27:43 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Ogre stun protection</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">It can be an advantage when pulling, particularly when sow'd. I typically pull running backwards, while attempting to slam the target. Never get stunned and do a little damage on occasion with melee/slam/riposte while luring the critter to my waiting friends. Plus it helps keep the critter mad at me, the tank, when the real fray begins.<br>
<br>
It also can be a life saver.. backing into the zone with a horde chasing you means you're not going to do the spinning dance of death.<br>
<br>
Nubb</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=95%><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessage?topicID=324.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1><< Prev Topic</FONT></A> &nbsp;<A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessage?topicID=288.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Next Topic >></FONT></A> </TD></TR></TABLE><BR><TABLE WIDTH=95% BORDER=0><TR><TD><A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=306.topic&index=3><IMG SRC=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0></A></TD><TD><A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.emailToFriend?topicID=306.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/images/email.gif BORDER=0 ALT="Email This To a Friend"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>&nbsp;Email This To a Friend</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.threadControl?topicID=306.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif BORDER=0 ALT="Topic Control Image"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;Topic Commands (Moderator only)</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=306.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Subscribe</FONT></A>  <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Click to receive email notification of replies</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=306.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Unsubscribe</FONT></A>  <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</FONT><BR></TD><TD></TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN=3 ALIGN=CENTER><BR><FORM ACTION=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum METHOD=POST><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Jump to: </FONT><SELECT NAME=forumName><OPTION VALUE=thesteelwarriorthearena>The Arena<OPTION VALUE=thesteelwar